# Claude Code: ignore local-only state + per-machine settings, but allow
# project skills/commands/protocol docs to be tracked. Skills are project
# knowledge (vendor-switch checklist, /go, /end-session, etc.) — they
# should be available to every Claude Code session, not just Petter's
# local machine.
